Stack: HTML/CSS/JS, Three.js, Microsoft Edge for development and testing
Target directory structure is defined in _map.md and is being built toward incrementally
app/js/ will contain extracted modules with specific responsibilities such as scene, controls, and surfaces
Each JS file in app/js/ must declare dependencies at the top and expose only what other modules need
Subfolders are only allowed for features with 3+ files of their own, with tools/ being the exception

